|-----|---------|------|
| `screen_home` | HomeScreen Scaffold | `ui/home/HomeScreen.kt` |
| `screen_search` | SearchScreen Scaffold | `ui/search/SearchScreen.kt` |
| `screen_map` | MapScreen Scaffold | `ui/map/MapScreen.kt` |
| `btn_menu` | Menu (hamburger) IconButton | `ui/home/HomeScreen.kt` |
